name: Fire with Fire Online Tower Attack and Defense
blurb: Fire with Fire is a Free to Play Cross Platform Online Player vs Player Tower Attack and Defense Game.

rewards.reward: BASIC BETA STARTER!\r\nYou will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of an in game tower set (5 towers) + all backers receive our stretch goals for free when we reach them!

WALLPAPER PACK!\r\nYou will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of an in game tower set and creep set (5 towers and 2 creeps) + a backer only 1920x1080 wallpaper + 5 game pins + 5 stickers. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

SOUNDTRACK PACK! You will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of an in game tower set and creep set(5 towers and 2 creeps) + our original sound track for the game as a digital download + the backer only wallpaper + 5 game pins + 5 stickers. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

POSTER PACK! You will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of an in game tower set and creep set (5 towers and 2 creeps) + an original signed by the team 11x17" poster + the backer only wallpaper + 5 game pins + 5 stickers. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

T-SHIRT PACK! You will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of two in game tower sets and one creep set (10 towers and 2 creeps) + a t-shirt featuring our backer voted favorite art peice + the backer only wallpaper + 5 game pins + 5 stickers. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

COMBO PACK! You will receive an invite to our Closed Beta + you can take your pick of two tower sets + two creep sets(10 towers and 4 creeps) + the t-shirt + the signed poster + the sound track + the backer only wallpaper + 5 game pins + 5 stickers. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

GUEST WRITER PACK\r\nEverything featured in the COMBO PACK plus directly help us create the atmosphere of Fire with Fire by writing out or helping us choose the flavor text of our creeps and towers. The text will be featured in game, will we will quote your username on the website and give out a unique forum label. Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.

GUEST DESIGNER PACK\r\nYou get everything from the COMBO PACK reward plus you are directly helping us create the levels, splash art and narrative for the story mode campaign. We will consult with you on the backstory and rely on your dictation for the look and feel of a key character featured though the cut scenes of the game. You will be listed as a character designer in our credits and receive 2 signed prints of the cut scene featuring your character(you should sign them also). Please add $10 for shipping outside the US.
